Paris(FYI the new season is out August 15th) as she's also in the marketing and creative field, so thought it was only natural to ask her for some insider spots to flee to during the Olympics for a few moments of peace and pleasure.\", \"from\": 328, \"to\": 597, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 365, \"end\": 370, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.816325699048861e-26, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 371, \"end\": 374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virgin_Media_Two\", \"score\": 0.9834401975926291, \"rank\": 0.016838645710361717, \"text\": \"FYI\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virgin_Media_Two\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virgin_Media_Two\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the new season\", \"from\": 375, \"to\": 389}, {\"ngram\": \"the marketing\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 440}, {\"ngram\": \"creative field\", \"from\": 445, \"to\": 459}, {\"ngram\": \"some insider spots\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 525}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 544, \"to\": 556}, {\"ngram\": \"a few moments\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 574}, {\"ngram\": \"peace\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 583}, {\"ngram\": \"pleasure\", \"from\": 588, \"to\": 596}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In this week leading up to the opening ceremony, Paris is quiet - eerily so, reminiscent of COVID-19 with no traffic in many of the streets,\\\" says Jackson, who notes there are clearly fewer visitors than anticipated and the restaurants are feeling it.\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 851, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 649, \"end\": 654, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.816325699048861e-26, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 692, \"end\": 700, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\", \"score\": 0.9999380026098795, \"rank\": 6.191603689176775e-05, \"text\": \"COVID-19\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\"}, {\"begin\": 747, \"end\": 754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Jackson\", \"score\": 0.9999999988654054, \"rank\": 1.1347383762899553e-09, \"text\": \"Jackson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Jackson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Jackson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this week\", \"from\": 603, \"to\": 612}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 647}, {\"ngram\": \"no traffic\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 716}, {\"ngram\": \"the streets\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 739}, {\"ngram\": \"fewer visitors\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 798}, {\"ngram\": \"the restaurants\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 835}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, some spots are even taking extended vacations because of the quietness.\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 932, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 859}, {\"ngram\": \"some spots\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 871}, {\"ngram\": \"extended vacations\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 906}, {\"ngram\": \"the quietness\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 931}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jackson recommends checking the Google listing or social media account of any restaurants and bars you plan on visiting as they could very well close earlier than the August holiday period.\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 1122, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 933, \"end\": 940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Jackson\", \"score\": 0.9999999988654054, \"rank\": 1.1347383762899553e-09, \"text\": \"Jackson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"htt