rom\": 1495, \"to\": 1505}, {\"ngram\": \"closed stations\", \"from\": 1509, \"to\": 1524}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now onto a few of Emily's favorite spots to bookmark for your next Paris visit: 54 rue d'Amsterdam 75009 (open all summer) \\\"Owned by a Canadian - who shares the bar's name thanks to her father, a fan of the prolific French writer Albert Camus - this newly-opened wine bar next to the Google offices offers a great selection of natural wines and craft cocktails (both Camus' favorites),\\\" says Jackson.\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1967, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1583, \"end\": 1588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emily_Fields\", \"score\": 0.9492699586363139, \"rank\": 0.05344071322173572, \"text\": \"Emily\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emily_Fields\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emily_Fields\"}, {\"begin\": 1632, \"end\": 1637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.816325699048861e-26, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1702, \"end\": 1710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.8958759198213201, \"rank\": 0.11358004692851226, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 1783, \"end\": 1789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9999837142420902, \"rank\": 1.5119239231559335e-05, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1851, \"end\": 1857, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.9796683841273884, \"rank\": 0.0207495248349921, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q4