 {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have had many a great night here just chatting and drinking and laughing with friends.\\\"\", \"from\": 2508, \"to\": 2598, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many a great night\", \"from\": 2520, \"to\": 2538}, {\"ngram\": \"friends\", \"from\": 2589, \"to\": 2596}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you are looking to hop around to a few places, she notesFuriaandBrasserie Martinare a quick five-minute stroll from Bar Principal.Insider tip: arrive early for a table outside.\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2778, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few places\", \"from\": 2635, \"to\": 2647}, {\"ngram\": \"a quick five-minute stroll\", \"from\": 2686, \"to\": 2712}, {\"ngram\": \"Bar Principal\", \"from\": 2718, \"to\": 2731}, {\"ngram\": \"Insider tip\", \"from\": 2732, \"to\": 2743}, {\"ngram\": \"a table\", \"from\": 2762, \"to\": 2769}]}, {\"sentence\": \"85 rue Jean-Pierre Timbaud \\\"[Bouche is] one of my personal coups de coeur (crushes) of recent months,\\\" says Jackson, who keeps returning for the food and the ambiance.\", \"from\": 2780, \"to\": 2948, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2889, \"end\": 2896, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Jackson\", \"score\": 0.9999999988654054, \"rank\": 1.1347383762899553e-09, \"text\": \"Jackson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Jackson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Jackson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"-Pierre\", \"from\": 2791, \"to\": 2798}, {\"ngram\": \"Bouche\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 2815}, {\"ngram\": \"crushes\", \"from\": 2855, \"to\": 2862}, {\"ngram\": \"recent months\", \"from\": 2867, \"to\": 2880}, {\"ngram\": \"the food\", \"from\": 2921, \"to\": 2929}, {\"ngram\": \"the ambiance\", \"from\": 2934, \"to\": 2946}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The menu is seasonal and changes based on what's available.\", \"from\": 2949, \"to\": 3008, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The menu\", \"from\": 2949, \"to\": 2957}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For summer expect dishes like duck terrine with pistachios and hazelnuts and a divine lobster roll with raspberry \\\"ketchup\\\" and basil.\", \"from\": 3009, \"to\": 3143, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"summer\", \"from\": 3013, \"to\": 3019}, {\"ngram\": \"dishes\", \"from\": 3027, \"to\": 3033}, {\"ngram\": \"duck terrine\", \"from\": 3039, \"to\": 3051}, {\"ngram\": \"pistachios\", \"from\": 3057, \"to\": 3067}, {\"ngram\": \"hazelnuts\", \"from\": 3072, \"to\": 3081}, {\"ngram\": \"a divine lobster roll\", \"from\": 3086, \"to\": 3107}, {\"ngram\": \"raspberry \\\"ketchup\", \"from\": 3113, \"to\": 3131}, {\"ngram\": \"basil\", \"from\": 3137, \"to\": 3142}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everyone I have ever taken here has always been as blown away as I have,\\\" she says.\", \"from\": 3144, \"to\": 3228, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everyone\", \"from\": 3145, \"to\": 3153}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The owners also just opened a second spot on the same street calledRoriwhich I am dying to try.\\\"\", \"from\": 3229, \"to\": 3326, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The owners\", \"from\": 3230, \"to\": 3240}, {\"ngram\": \"a second spot\", \"from\": 3258, \"to\": 3271}, {\"ngram\": \"the same street\", \"from\": 3275, \"to\": 3290}, {\"ngram\": \"calledRoriwhich\", \"from\": 3291, \"to\": 3306}]}, {\"sentence\": \"4 rue Viollet le Duc 75009 \\\"Piloted by the dynamic duo behindRed Housein the 11th arrondissement, Jen Riley and Joe Boley, this bar is a fan favorite both for its stellar cocktails and its drag nights,\\\" says Jackson.\", \"from\": 3328, \"to\": 3545, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3431, \"end\": 3436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riley_Finn\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.502624298803152e-12, \"text\": \"Riley\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riley_Finn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riley_Finn\"}, {\"begin\": 3441, \"end\": 3444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\", \"score\": 0.5795877862681976, \"rank\": 0.7239766315570589, \"text\": \"Joe\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\"}, {\"begin\": 3445, \"end\": 3450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boley,_Oklahoma\", \"score\": 0.9500883482672277, \"rank\": 0.03333333333334321, \"text\": \"Boley\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boley,_Oklahoma\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boley,_Oklahoma\"}, {\"begin\": 3537, \"end\": 3544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Jackson\", \"score\": 0.9999999988654054, \"rank\": 1.1347383762899553e-09, \"text\": \"Jackson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Jackson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Jackson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Duc\", \"from\": 3345, \"to\": 3348}, {\"ngram\": \"the dynamic duo\", \"from\": 3367, \"to\": 3382}, {\"ngram\": \"behindRed Housein\", \"from\": 3383, \"to\": 3400}, {\"ngram\": \"the 11th arrondissement\", \"from\": 3401, \"to\": 3424}, {\"ngram\": \"this bar\", \"from\": 3451, \"to\": 3459}, {\"ngram\": \"its stellar cocktails\", \"from\": 3487, \"to\": 3508}, {\"ngram\": \"its drag nights\", \"from\": 3513, \"to\": 3528}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They do switch up the menu so my favorite is no longer on it (a gin-based marvel called the Violet Chachki), but you are guaranteed to find something you will enjoy,\\\" she says.\", \"from\": 3546, \"to\": 3723, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the menu\", \"from\": 3565, \"to\": 3573}, {\"ngram\": \"my favorite\", \"from\": 3577, \"to\": 3588}, {\"ngram\": \"a gin-based marvel\", \"from\": 3609, \"to\